title: Waiting
lyrics:
I’m fine in the dark
I’m right where I should be
Don’t try to fix me
The devil’s speakin to me
End my life in my sleep

I hide til the pain stops

The only way I cant feel



You said I was the only one

Never speak now I feel alone

I want you I want me I want we I want us to be seen again

Your veins always flowing cold

Tell me you just wanna be alone

I want you I want me I want we I want us to be seen again



Don’t speak to, me, no

Don’t think we’ll, be, no

Don’t play with me, no

Don’t wait for, no
